{"tid":1905050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無辜被罵台獨！子瑜低調捐30萬助內地抗疫","createTime":"2020-03-01T03:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:01:21.000Z","uid":212884,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41fd8572df8aaf9d7d793cb3dc1de0f75629bac8","tid":1905050,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOFesZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOFesZx.png&h=dde67acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓新冠肺炎確診病例迅速破3,000，不少韓星亦陸續捐款抗疫，而韓團TWICE的台灣成員周子瑜亦透過當地社會福利共同募捐會，捐款約32萬港元支援抗疫，獲韓國網民大讚她人美心善，但有內地網友卻鬧爆她未有優先捐款予最先爆出疫情的內地，更大罵她是「台獨」。<br />\n不過，昨晚內地微博「暖流計劃」貼出感謝子瑜捐款30萬人民幣抗疫的感謝狀：「感謝TWICE組合成員周子瑜通過@周子瑜吧_TZUYUbar 捐贈善款30萬元人民幣，支持暖流計劃疫情防控，捐款將主要用於採購醫用防護面罩」內地網友獲悉子瑜原來有低調捐款予內地抗疫即改口大讚她暖心，可憐子瑜之前卻無辜捱罵！<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/GvGlvY?utm_source=washare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FGvGlvY%3Futm_source%3Dwashare&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGogmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=75ea145f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/GvGlvY?utm_source=washare</a>"},{"pid":"27d9972e5185b5c81728edc1979d756ccb35df90","tid":1905050,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"支瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7078f0271f62b8fd42691415e4a9abd25c4af0d4","tid":1905050,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"ae99a1cfc433f67840de609c6dfa76bdab1f5e6a","tid":1905050,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7078f0271f62b8fd42691415e4a9abd25c4af0d4","tid":1905050,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"支瑜"},{"pid":"568145f8bb4dc2090a98b7b0f90a1cd70781d43d","tid":1905050,"uid":2